  "scientific_question": "In a two-mode, single-pair truncation of a scalar field on a prescribed expanding FLRW-like background, what particle-number and pair-correlation observables are produced by an explicit stepwise time-dependent evolution, and how accurately do exact local and noisy local estimator workflows reproduce the benchmark?\n",
